CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 14, 1953 reads: "Razing Old Church To Build Anew - Members of St. Paul Baptist congregation observe joyfully the razing of their old church edifice on Broad Street between Evaline and Pacific Avenues in picture (1) because it brings nearer their dream of the new church on the same sport... Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Crowd watching the razing of St. Paul Baptist Church, Broad Street
